  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to gnash</title>

    <para>
      <application>Gnash</application> is the GNU Flash movie player and browser
      plugin. This is useful for watching YouTube videos or simple flash
      animations.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked;

